 490:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *
 491:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *  This function controls the external Power Amplifier and Low Noise Amplifier
