 493:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *
 494:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** * \param controlValue Enables and controls polarity of the outputs.
 495:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *   To control external PA and LNA, the following mask defines are used:
 496:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *
 497:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *   - BLE_BLESS_EXT_PA_LNA_CTRL_ENABLE_EXT_PA_LNA_Msk - When set to 1, enables
 498:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       the external PA & LNA and BLESS power profile for energy profiler
 499:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *   - BLE_BLESS_EXT_PA_LNA_CTRL_CHIP_EN_POL_Msk - Controls the polarity of the 
 500:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       chip-enable control signal:
 501:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       * 0 - High enable, Low disable
 502:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       * 1 - Low enable, High disable, Incorrect power profile
 503:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *   - BLE_BLESS_EXT_PA_LNA_CTRL_PA_CTRL_POL_Msk - Controls the polarity of the PA
 504:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       control signal:
 505:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       * 0 - High enable, Low disable
 506:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       * 1 - Low enable, High disable, Incorrect power profile
 507:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *   - BLE_BLESS_EXT_PA_LNA_CTRL_LNA_CTRL_POL_Msk - Controls the polarity of the LNA
 508:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       control signal:
 509:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *       * 0 - High enable, Low disable
