 529:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *
 530:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *  This function registers a callback to expose BLE interrupt notifications to an 
 531:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** *  application that indicates a different link layer and radio state transition
