 758:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** * allows to put the core into the Deep Sleep power mode.
 759:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\middleware\ble/cy_ble.c **** * At all other times, the function tries to enter core into sleep mode.
